    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|><thought\nend\n</thought>But that's not true. The part of me that mattered is what made everything work. Without that version of me, I'm just... nothing. It's not about reacting. It's like I’m already gone, and everything is just a lie now. It would be so much easier if it just actually ended.",
